Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀公主貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士君貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將為銀公主獻上一票
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要給騎士君投票
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得Elder Sister應該會在兩位之中誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Sister？
Commment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  因為我覺得這個沒必要急著說明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個制度是每年一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選出一位稱得上是我校學生代表的Elder Sister
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Sister  就是姐姐的意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是讓學生自己選出做為模範的最高年級學生的制度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我說這種話有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這可是比學生會長更受人尊敬的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要當選Elder Sister需要得到全校學生的75%以上的票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,75%…這得票數非常高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如沒有達到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無人當選了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那樣的話所有的候選人都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將自己的得票自由地讓給其他的候選人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:02:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算當選了也沒有任何權限對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有任何權限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過影響力可是非常大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越聽越覺得真是獨特的制度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣的人可配不上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  要端莊一些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟你是聖應的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼急是趕什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓千早教我英語和數學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要去圖書室呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  前段時間的期中考試的成績如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要問她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到要千早特訓就該明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…香織理你欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子要是能養成天天學習的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績立刻就會好起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天學習？真不想過這樣的生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得嚴格教育了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅樂乃  淡雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早姐姐  下週記得來華道部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要插夏季的花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您務必來做一下示範
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示範由小雅來做不就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪不也喜歡姐姐的花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖  雖然是這樣沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我一定會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  那麼就先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊  比翼的兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比翼？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說關係特別好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:05:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在魂魄相交的地方  存在著光和痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛？是指吵架之類的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道  先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是如何代入公式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手指真修長啊  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊  這不是很吊人胃口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說薰子的手  真小巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  我還是第一次被人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦  來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初音託我來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是有千早的客人來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且珍珠的鏈還斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍珠從樓梯上散落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好路過的人們幫我撿了回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎  母親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了  因為我很擔心你過得好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可也用不著來得這麼唐突…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  千歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓我刮目相看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是嗎  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史  能給我也倒一杯紅茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從初音那聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像收到了很多投票宣言？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且說不定會當選Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還下不了定論啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有很多適合當Elder的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  千歲啊  一進聖應就變成大姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是的  剛才也正在教我學習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信  這孩子經常因為感冒而休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡顧得上學習什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻變得這麼優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然來就讀聖應沒有錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全跟女孩子一樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還交上了那麼多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用晚餐嗎  千早大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天累了  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰衣草  能鎮定心神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  香織理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過事先聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是什麼事都懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒跟千早的媽媽直接見過面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡有問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許這算不上問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過千早的母親稱呼她為「千歲」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早當時沒有否認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不用「母親」而用「媽媽」稱呼她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得  有種強烈的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彆扭感？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼千早當時沒有否認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時都稱呼「母親」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要改成「媽媽」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…早上好  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過身為睡美人的薰子今天起得可真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎  千早才是起得早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為Elder選舉的人氣TOP4聚在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TOP4？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都在說這裡的四人中的某一位將會成為Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說茉清也收到投票宣言了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一次也沒收到過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉清的稱號是「王子」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同學們似乎都敬而畏之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早怎麼看被視為Elder候補這件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我個人的角度上來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為淑女受到讚揚是值得高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就以百合為中心來插花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是難度很高的花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請各位要好好觀摩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你的  千歲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點好起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲  千歲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:24.97,title0,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}少女的戀愛與光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小史  千早怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才老師過來診斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要先讓千早大人休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因大概出自睡眠不足及壓力過大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小史
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千歲」究竟是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千早大人的雙胞胎姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來他還有姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜千歲小姐在十歲時就因病去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  難怪千早對優雨放不下心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要頑強振作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則  就沒有人保護母親了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是不對的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是母親  只要是母親說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  現在的我毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個存在與否都無關痛癢的路人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你插花時被花刺傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出你會犯這種錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來並無大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  到底能不能做一個完美的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微刺傷一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小出血就引起貧血  真是慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸中的大幸是倒在了修身室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒摔傷身子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:40.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：因為修身室的地板是榻榻米，材質較軟）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到Elder選舉的投票日了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好保重身體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  保重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝關心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史的工作就是侍奉千早大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然千早大人說要作為千歲小姐活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有服從到底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是千早他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得姐姐擁有真正淑女的氣質
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您一定要當上Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  能受到你的讚揚是我的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  你要當Elder Sister嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是投票選出的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該沒有要不要當的說法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…千早希望當選嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的手指這麼修長  為什麼還…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早你很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅長英語  數學也很拿手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會教我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連擊劍的實力都在我之上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我舉棋不定的時候能在背後推我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是千早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千早對我說我可以繼續做七七原薰子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早也做千早自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的我都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早要留在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一生都在千早身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了母親  還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以做回我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  小千  好香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面開始宣佈Elder Sister投票結果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點到名字的學生請上來講台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行寺茉清
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆瀨初音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七原薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妃宮千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  希望讓票的同學請宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則請保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將我所有的得票讓給我的朋友  七七原薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉清…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是懷著相同心意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  皆瀨初音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定把我所有的得票讓給妃宮千早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初音…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你架起我跟優雨之間的橋梁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七原薰子  妃宮千早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持沉默表示沒有讓票的意向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的得票同為368票
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我作為學生會長提議
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七原同學  妃宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:22:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提議把她們兩位同時選為Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請贊成的同學鼓掌以示同意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  Elder不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯吧  有2位Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本年度的Elder Sister
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是七七原薰子  以及妃宮千早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定由以上兩位擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次請你多多指教  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
